\\\Rightarrow\qquad 25(4b+19)&=19(6b+11)
\\\Rightarrow\qquad 100b+475&=114b+209
\\\Rightarrow\qquad -14b&=-266
\\\Rightarrow\qquad b&=\boxed{19}
\end{align*}. Final Answer: 19

